    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2758065/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2758065/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">[已注销]</span>
    </a>  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-11-01"
      class="main-meta">2008-11-01 23:57:13</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1542778_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  我一直不认为吕后这个人足够出一本书,拿到这本书后我就知道自己没错了,字体很大,页面够空,硬加上一些图片,终于可以成一本厚厚的书了! 王老师讲史一向都是条理清晰,分析也比较到位.让我们全方位了解吕后这个人.不过就如同讲项羽反复说项很会打仗,政治上却极幼稚一样,此书太多重...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1542778/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1542778_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1542778_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
